reviewText: It arrived on time and in great condition. It played well and enjoyed it.  Thank you.

Excellent movie. Slightly better than Assault on Devil's Island. If you look at the titles that the studios put on the covers, they say Shadow Warriors and Shadow Warriors 2: Assault on Devil's Island.  The titles should be switched, because Assault on Devil's Island is the first in the series.

I really wish Hulk had been successful in his acting career. He is really quite decent. And sans mustache with the hair piece he really becomes someone else. Carl Weathers is always awesome and Shannon tweed is great (in a rare non nude role too!) Give it a try. Its a rarity.
I have to say, I'm happy with this one for good quality,right price and fast deliver. Not much more I can add other than it do the job it is meant to do.
